The site is located about five minutes by car from [[:en:Matsuzaki Station (Tottori)|Matsuzaki Station]] on the [[:en:West Japan Railway Company|West Japan Railway Company]] [[San'in Main Line]].<ref name="Shiseki"/>
;Overall length: 110 meters ;Posterior circular portion: 70 meter diameter x 12 meters high ;Anterior rectangular portion: 62 meters long x 5.5 to 9.5meters high ;"neck" portion: 43 meters wide
